                  </persName> were indicted for<rs id="t18430102-536-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18430102-536-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18430102-536-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> steal<lb></lb>ing, on the <rs id="t18430102-cd-119" type="crimeDate">
